POST	/api/storymaps	创建新的校园故事地图：
示例请求体：
{
  "title": "New Story Map",
  "description": "This is a new map.",
  "coverImageUrl": "http://...",
  "locations": [
    {
      "lat": 34.0522,
      "lng": -118.2437,
      "title": "Location 1",
      "description": "Details...",
      "imageUrl": "http://..."
    }
  , ...
  ]
}
需要返回的格式：
{
  "storyMapId": "uuid-string",
  "title": "New Story Map",
  "description": "This is a new map.",
  "authorId": "uuid-string",
  "createdAt": "timestamp",
  "coverImageUrl": "http://...",
  "locations": [ ... ]
}